snippet.title: Rival Pirates - Launch Trailer - Netflix, iOS, Android
snippet.description:
Avast mateys! Take to the high seas in frenetic multiplayer fun with Rival Pirates. Fire cannons and swashbuckle with friends to see who rules the ocean. Free to play for all Netflix subscribers.

Developed by: Amuzo Games
